song_lyrics: Shyām sanehī gher āvyā Ghanshyām āvyā,
Hete Hari gher āvyā re, Shyām sanehī gher āvyā Ghanshyam... Ṭek
Sāmaiyu laīne Shyām sundarne, monghe motīḍe vadhāvyā... Ghanshyām 1
Dūdhaḍe charaṇ pakhāḷyā Prabhunā, pāṭ upar padharāvyā... Ghanshyām 2
Bangalā upar bāndhī hinḍoḷo, Harivarne hīchakāvyā... Ghanshyām 3
Premānandno Nāth manohar, Mahārāj māre man bhāvyā... Ghanshyām 4
title: Shyām sanehī gher āvyā Ghanshyām āvyā
